Package: lcfstat
Title: A Uniformly Bounded Correlation Function for Spatial Point Patterns
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Evgenia", "Martynova", , "evg.martynova@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0461-1787"))
Description: A function to compute the local correlation function for spatial point 
    patterns, that measure of the degree of clustering in a point pattern and has 
    a bounded and interpretable scale.
